reviewText: Could not get one to play at all!

I love Army Wives!!! I have every single season to date and even pre-order them. I purchased these items used, received them in the mail and they looked like they had never been touched! They were in excellent condition and I have absolutely no complaint. (: One happy client here!!!

I was thrilled to be able to purchase 3 seasons at once.  I couldn't wait go get these in the mail so I could catch up on what was going on with my favorite characters.  Great way to spend a rainy day.
I received the purchase in a timely manner and was very pleased with the DVD's.  I would order from this company again.
